          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3899677-sheric-pm?shelf=6-ft-possible">6-ft-possible</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3899677-sheric-pm?shelf=0-tossed-it">0-tossed-it</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3899677-sheric-pm?shelf=4-format-paperback">4-format-paperback</a>, 
